\c 16
\nb
\v 1 Kwathi uDavida esedlule kancinyane engqongeni\x + 15.30,32.\x*, khangela, uZiba inceku kaMefiboshethi wamhlangabeza elabobabhemi ababili belezihlalo\x + 9.2-12.\x*, bethwele izinkwa ezingamakhulu amabili, lamahlukuzo alikhulu ezithelo ezonyisiweyo zevini\x + 1 Sam. 25.18.\x*, lezithelo zehlobo ezilikhulu, lomgodla wewayini\x + Isa. 16.9. Jer. 40.10,12.\x*.
\v 2 Inkosi yasisithi kuZiba: Uthini \add nga\add*lezizinto? UZiba wasesithi: Obabhemi ngabendlu yenkosi ukuthi bagade, lezinkwa lezithelo zehlobo ngezamajaha ukuthi adle\x + Gen. 33.8.\x*, lewayini ngelabaphelelwa ngamandla enkangala ukuthi banathe\x + 16.14. 17.29.\x*.
\v 3 Inkosi yasisithi: Pho, ingaphi indodana yenkosi yakho? UZiba wasesithi enkosini: Khangela, uhlezi eJerusalema, ngoba uthe: Lamuhla uIsrayeli uzabuyisela kimi umbuso kababa\x + 19.26,27.\x*.
\v 4 Inkosi yasisithi kuZiba: Khangela, ngokwakho konke okukaMefiboshethi. UZiba wasesithi: Ngiyakhothama; kangithole umusa emehlweni akho, nkosi yami, nkosi.
\p
\v 5 Kwathi inkosi uDavida ifika eBahurimi\x + 3.16.\x*, khangela, kwaphuma khona umuntu wosendo lwendlu kaSawuli, obizo lakhe linguShimeyi indodana kaGera\x + 19.16. 1 Kho. 2.8,44.\x*; waphuma, ehamba\f + \fk ehamba: \fl Heb. \fqa ephuma\f* ethuka.
\v 6 Wasejikijela uDavida ngamatshe kanye lenceku zonke zenkosi uDavida, labo bonke abantu lamaqhawe wonke ngakwesokunene sakhe langakwesokhohlo sakhe.
\v 7 Wasesitsho njalo uShimeyi ekuthukeni kwakhe: Phuma, phuma, muntu wegazi, muntu kaBheliyali\x + Dute. 13.13.\x*!
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* ibuyisele phezu kwakho\x + 1 Kho. 2.32. Hlu. 9.24,56,57. 1 Kho. 2.33.\x* lonke igazi lendlu kaSawuli obubusa esikhundleni sakhe; iN\nd kosi\nd* inikele umbuso esandleni sikaAbisalomu indodana yakho. Khangela, usebubini bakho, ngoba ungumuntu omele igazi\x + 1.16. 3.28,29. 4.11,12.\x*.
\p
\v 9 UAbishayi indodana kaZeruya wasesithi enkosini: Linja efileyo iyithukelani inkosi yami, inkosi? Ake ngedlule ngisuse ikhanda layo\x + 9.8. 3.8.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa inkosi yathi: Ngilani lani\x + 19.22. 1 Kho. 17.18. 2 Kho. 3.13. 2 Lan. 35.21. Ezra 4.3. Mat. 8.29. Mark. 1.24. Luka 4.34. 8.28. Joha. 2.4.\x*, madodana kaZeruya\x + 1 Sam. 26.6.\x*? Ngakho kathuke, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ithe kuye: Thuka uDavida; pho, ngubani ozakuthi: Wenzeleni njalo?
\v 11 UDavida wasesithi kuAbishayi lakuzo zonke inceku zakhe: Khangela, indodana yami, ephume emibilini yami, idinga impilo yami; kangakanani-ke lumBhenjamini? Myekeleni, athuke, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumile kuye\x + Gen. 15.4.\x*.
\v 12 Mhlawumbe iN\nd kosi\x + 2 Kho. 19.4.\x*\nd* izabona usizi lwami, iN\nd kosi\nd* ingibuyisele okuhle esikhundleni sokuthuka kwakhe lamuhla\x + Gen. 29.32.\x*.
\v 13 UDavida labantu bakhe basebehamba ngendlela; loShimeyi ehamba eceleni kwentaba maqondana laye, ehamba ethuka, emjikijela ngamatshe, e\add m\add*thela ngothuli.
\v 14 Inkosi labo bonke abantu ababelayo bafika sebekhathele; yasihlumelela khona.
\p
\v 15 UAbisalomu labantu bonke, amadoda akoIsrayeli, basebefika eJerusalema, loAhithofeli elaye\x + 15.37.\x*.
\v 16 Kwasekusithi lapho uHushayi umArki\x + 15.37. Josh. 16.2.\x*, umngane kaDavida, esefike kuAbisalomu, uHushayi wathi kuAbisalomu: Kayiphile inkosi! Kayiphile inkosi!
\v 17 UAbisalomu wasesithi kuHushayi: Yiwo umusa wakho kumngane wakho yini? Kungani ungahambanga lomngane wakho\x + 19.25.\x*?
\v 18 UHushayi wasesithi kuAbisalomu: Hatshi, kodwa lowo emkhethayo iN\nd kosi\nd*, lalababantu, lawo wonke amadoda akoIsrayeli, ngizakuba ngowakhe, njalo ngihlale laye.
\v 19 Ngokwesibili, mina ngizakhonza bani? Kungabi phambi kobuso bendodana yakhe na? Njengoba ngakhonza phambi kukayihlo, ngokunjalo ngizakuba phambi kwakho\x + 15.34.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UAbisalomu wasesithi kuAhithofeli: Phanini iseluleko senu ukuthi sizakwenza njani?
\v 21 UAhithofeli wasesithi kuAbisalomu: Ngena kubafazi abancane bakayihlo abatshiye ukulinda indlu\x + 15.16. 20.3.\x*; loIsrayeli wonke uzakuzwa ukuthi ulevumba kuyihlo\x + 10.6. 1 Sam. 13.4.\x*; khona izandla zabo bonke abalawe zizaqina\x + 2.7. Zek. 8.9,13.\x*.
\v 22 Basebemendlalela uAbisalomu ithente phezu kophahla\x + 11.2.\x*; uAbisalomu wasengena kubafazi abancane bakayise phambi kwamehlo kaIsrayeli wonke\x + 12.11,12.\x*.
\v 23 Iseluleko sikaAhithofeli aseluleka ngalezonsuku sasinjengomuntu ebuza ilizwi likaNkulunkulu; sasinjalo sonke iseluleko sikaAhithofeli kubo bobabili uDavida loAbisalomu\x + 15.12.\x*.